 3. the person who's sport is handball is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
 7. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
 8. the owner of the dog is the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the owner of the goat is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
10. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person watching drama movies##2
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
13. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
14. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

