 4. the australian is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking milk##7
 7. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
 8. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is hiking##7
 9. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
10. the canadian is not to the left of the canadian##8
11. the mexican is on the far left##1
12. the french is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the trike is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
14. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
15. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
16. the canadian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##8

.:: Answer ::.
