There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, green, white, mauve
 1. the owner of the goldfish is not the fan of rock##6
 2. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the person who likes green##7
 3. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of punk##1
 4. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
 5. the person who likes turquise is between the person who likes white and the fan of salsa##2
 6. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 7. the owner of the dog is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
 9. the person who likes green is not the owner of the goldfish##6
10. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the person who likes turquise##8
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
14. the fan of folk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |    3     |   4    |
