.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-11::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, cranberry, pear, strawberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, electronic, jazz, punk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, october, december, june
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, hedgehog, horse
 1. the person eating pear is not the fan of electronic##6
 2. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the fan of punk and the owner of the ferret##7
 3. the owner of the ferret is not the person who's birthday is in june##6
 4. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of electronic##5
 5. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 7. the fan of jazz is between the fan of blues and the person eating cranberry##2
 8. the person eating strawberry is in an odd position##4
 9. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the fan of blues##8
10. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
11. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
12. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
13. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the person eating cranberry##8
14. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
15. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
