.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, milk, sprite
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, dahlia, aconite, amaryllis
4 different pets are kept: goat, hedgehog, pony, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, subway, van
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 2. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the person who growsdahlia##8
 3. the owner of the goat is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
 6. the person driving the van is the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
 9. the person who growsdahlia is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
12. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
13. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | juice          | iced-tea | milk        | sprite    |
| Flower         | amaryllis | balloon-flower   | dahlia | aconite  |
| Pet         | pony           | goat     | snake       | hedgehog  |
| Transport   | van            | subway   | scooter     | quad-bike |

