.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, singing, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, social-worker, teacher
City: hannover, edinburgh, colone, berlin
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, jazz, reggae
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the bartender##8
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 3. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 4. the teacher is the person traveling to berlin##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the social-worker##6
 6. the person traveling to hannover is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is not to the left of the social-worker##8
 8. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
10. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
11. the person traveling to hannover is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the social-worker and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku    | singing   | board-games   | collecting |
| Job           | bartender | doctor    | social-worker | teacher    |
| City   | colone   | hannover | edinburgh     | berlin    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | jazz      | indie         | reggae     |

 